    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=# N8N Workflow Error Email Prompt\n\nCreate an internal email to report a workflow error using the following n8n execution data:\n\n## Data Structure\n- execution.id: {{ $json.execution.id }}\n- execution.url: {{ $json.execution.url }}\n- execution.mode: {{ $json.execution.mode }}\n- error.message: {{ $json.execution.error.message }}\n- error.stack: {{ $json.execution.error.stack }}\n- execution.lastNodeExecuted: {{ $json.execution.lastNodeExecuted }}\n- workflow.id: {{ $json.workflow.id }}\n- workflow.name: {{ $json.workflow.name }}\n- date: {{ $now.format('yyyy-MM-dd') }}\n\n## Output Format Required\n```\nSUBJECT: [Clear, concise subject line]\n\nBODY:\n[Email body content - plain text with line breaks for HTML template]\n```\n\n## Email Requirements\n- This is for sending via n8n's Send Email node with HTML template\n- From: n8n Automation Team\n- Internal team notification only\n- Tone: Direct and technical\n- Include clickable n8n execution link for quick debugging\n- Highlight if this is a retry failure (indicates persistent issue)\n- Focus on immediate action items for developers\n- Body should be formatted for HTML display (use line breaks and simple formatting)\n- Use workflow and node names for easy identification\n- Keep subject concise for email header\n- Body content will be inserted into HTML template with styling\n\nGenerate the email in the exact SUBJECT/BODY format for n8n email automation with HTML template.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "batching": {}
      },
